lead_paragraph: England under-21 coach Gareth Southgate looks likely to be put in temporary charge of the national team after the resignation of Roy Hodgson following the side's Euro 2016 exit, British media reported on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Southgate Set to Be England Temporary Manager, Media Say
headline.main: Southgate Set to Be England Temporary Manager, Media Say
